/E (Vastukrit Architects is an emerging architecture and planning practice based in Udaipur, dedicated to designing context-responsive built environments across residential, hospitality, commercial, and institutional domains. The studio believes architecture should emerge from climate, culture, and spatial logic while addressing contemporary aspirations. Through a balance of regional identity, material expression, and functional precision, the firm develops architectural solutions that are sustainable, experiential, and deeply connected to place.)
