/Type /StructElem
/S /P
/P 81 0 R
/E (At Vastukrit Architects, design is approached as a balance between context, climate, and contemporary living. The firm believes architecture should evolve from the specific conditions of each site, responding to environmental behavior, cultural identity, and user requirements. Through careful attention to proportion, material expression, natural light, and spatial organization, each project is developed to achieve functional efficiency and experiential quality. The objective is to create architecture that is rooted in place, technically sound, and capable of offering long-term value.)
/Pg 11 0 R
/K [3]
>>
